des:
Eagleyes is the first ProAV solution allows you to control HDMI network extenders, A/V matrixes, digital power supplies and other connected devices.

To use Eagle Eyes services, you must have a valid Intrising Eagle Eyes account. 
You can use this skill after login and can do nothing without login.
